section.section:
The owner of a motor vehicle, or a lessee of the vehicle under a lease not intended as security, or a director, officer, employee, or partner of a business entity that owns the vehicle may apply to the Administration for the assignment of a special registration number and special registration plates under this section for a vehicle included in one of the following classes:
A Class A (passenger) vehicle;
A Class E (truck) vehicle with a one ton or less manufacturer's rated capacity;
A Class M (multipurpose) vehicle; or
A Class D (motorcycle) vehicle.
